FBIS4-59546 "drnes094_j_94038" FBIS-NES-94-094 Daily Report 15 May 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Unity Celebrations To Be Held in All Governorates Unity Celebrations To Be Held in All Governorates JN1505132894 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 1200 GMT 15 May 94 JN1505132894 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network Arabic BFN [Text] The higher committee charged with preparing for the festivals marking the fourth anniversary of the Yemeni Republic met this morning under brother Deputy Prime Minister 'Abd-al-Wahhab al- Anisi. During this meeting, the conferees discussed the timetable for the celebrations of the Republic's national day, the fourth anniversary of unity and the establishment of the Yemen Republic. Despite the difficult circumstances brought about by the gang of apostasy and secession in the Socialist Party, the committee decided to hold festivals to mark this dear anniversary in all governorates in the country; the anniversary of the day on which our people's dream and great goal -- the restoration of unity and the establishment of the Yemeni Republic -- was achieved on 22 May 1990.
